Package fi.tamk.yourtrueself

Contains game core logic.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AchievementListener
    Callback interface for achievement completion tracking.
    ChallengeCompletedListener
    Callback for completed challenges.
    YTSTimerHelper
    Helper interface for platform-specific background timer methods.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Achievement
    Achievement for the player to complete.
    AchievementManager
    Helper class to manage achievements, their progress, completion, loading and saving.
    Challenge
    Challenge data.
    Character
    Character information.
    DailyChallenge
    Daily challenge.
    DefaultPreferences
    Container class for preferences related constants
    Player
    Represents the player of the game.
    TieredAchievement
    A multi-tier achievement.
    YTSChallenges
    Container class for the game's challenges
    YTSGame
    ApplicationListener implementation shared by all platforms.
    YTSSkin
    Custom Skin class that adds support for .ttf fonts.
    YTSSkinLoader
    Custom Skin loader that creates a YTSSkin.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Player.Stat
    Enum representing all the stats and "none" for no stat.
